claim.claim-text:
1. A method comprising:
a) outputting through a display device responsive to operation of a computer, indicia corresponding to a cash dispensing automated banking machine including a card reader operative to read data from cards and to utilize the data read from cards by the card reader, wherein the indicia includes a graphical representation of a visual appearance of the automated banking machine, wherein the graphical representation shows a visual appearance of a plurality of hardware devices included in the automated banking machine;
b) receiving with the computer, data indicative of a condition of at least one of the plurality of hardware devices included in the automated banking machine;
c) outputting through the display device responsive to operation of the computer, indicia representative of which of the plurality of hardware devices is associated with the condition.

7. Computer readable media, including computer executable instructions, wherein the instructions are operative to cause a computer to carry out a method comprising:
a) outputting through a display device responsive to operation of the computer, indicia corresponding to a cash dispensing automated banking machine including a card reader operative to read data from cards and to utilize data read from cards by the card reader, wherein the indicia includes a graphical representation of a visual appearance of the automated banking machine, wherein the graphical representation shows a visual appearance of a plurality of hardware devices included in the automated banking machine;
b) receiving with the computer, data indicative of a condition of at least one of the plurality of hardware devices included in the automated banking machine;
c) outputting through the display device responsive to operation of the computer, indicia representative of which of the plurality of hardware devices is associated with the condition.
